Donna Hussey has been branded a 'bad mum' by trolls on Facebook over death of her son Freddie . 
  Three-year-old was killed when a runaway trailer crushed him against a wall in Bristol . 
  Trailer used as a workmen's cabin came loose from a passing Land Rover . 
  Mrs Hussey was helpless as trailer mounted pavement and crushed her son . 
  Tony Davies was spared jail after admitting causing death by careless driving . 
  She has been targeted on Facebook and branded a ‘bad mum’ by trolls . 
  Mr Hussey also blasted Davies’ six-month driving ban and 200 hours of community service as a 'joke' Freddie was crushed to death in Bedminster in January last year . 
 